# =============================================
# .cursorrules — УЗЕЛОК64 (uzelok64.ru)
# Project Rules for Cursor AI
# =============================================

## 📋 Project Overview
- **Project**: uzelok64.ru — multi-brand product showcase + engineering-sewing workshop
- **Brands**:
  - БАТЯ (BATYA) — household goods / хозтовары
  - БУЙ (BUY) — auto/moto/water transport accessories
  - ВОЛНА (VOLNA) — hunting, fishing, tourism
- **Workshop**: Engineering-sewing workshop in Solnechny (Saratov) — pattern engineering, prototype creation
- **Business model**: Direct sales from own site (bypass Ozon commission); fallback — redirect to Ozon product page
- **Hosting**: Beget (PHP 8.4), deploy via Git + GitHub Actions

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- **Backend**: PHP 8.4 (pure PHP, NO frameworks)
  - Use: Enums, Readonly properties, Constructor promotion, match expressions, named arguments
  - PSR-4 autoloading via Composer
- **Database**: SQLite (single file at `database/uzelok64.db`)
- **Frontend**: Tailwind CSS (CDN for dev, compiled for production)
  - Vanilla JS for interactivity (no jQuery, no React, no Vue)
  - `<dialog>` element for modals
- **Integrations**:
  - Ozon Seller API (product sync)
  - Telegram Bot API (order notifications)
- **No frameworks**: Do NOT use Laravel, Symfony, Slim, Yii, or any PHP framework
- **No JS frameworks**: Do NOT use React, Vue, Angular, jQuery

